c=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n安度因咪個仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n瓦里安就真係死左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c026be5b1e8bb3981407cc85a4bf5eeb7a57d1dc","tid":457462,"uid":66433,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T18:53:55.000Z","msg":"其實不如wow重製啦 雖然畫面見做一路有改善但今時今日d畫面仲咁粗糙我玩左十幾年見到其他game以家咁靚真係唔想再玩wow<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"445769059aa857aefc06204ec807d95b06a6e3e5","tid":457462,"uid":116530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T19:02:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實不如wow重製啦 雖然畫面見做一路有改善但今時今日d畫面仲咁粗糙我玩左十幾年見到其他game以家咁靚真係唔想再玩wow<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n粗糙？自己入Game睇下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63646335e717bfa74c887ef582357d5cede55a0b","tid":457462,"uid":66433,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T19:46:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實不如wow重製啦 雖然畫面見做一路有改善但今時今日d畫面仲咁粗糙我玩左十幾年見到其他game以家咁靚真係唔想再玩wow<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n粗糙？自己入Game睇下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我係出阿古斯前afk乜阿古斯patch畫面靚左好多咩? 做唔做到destint2既畫質?destiny2普通spec電腦都推得掂 同一部電腦推畫質靚過魔獸好多 如果wow做到咁月費貴多一倍我都會玩<br />\n仲有另一個我認為要重製既原因係台服以家變左死城但由於暴雪係第一日出魔獸開始已經限死左台服同美服有唔同既terms and conditions所以d野冇可能互通到 後期出既overwatch就醒啦 同一個ac無論亞/美/歐服ac資料都係互通 魔獸可以咁既話肯定keep到果班見以家台服冇乜人冇心機再玩又唔想去美服重新升過既玩家"},{"pid":"c3da4d53b0557a801795a4a99eb068547b517706","tid":457462,"uid":92296,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T20:05:02.000Z","msg":"女王已經唔夠霸氣 仲加